# Starlette CVE exceptions reviewed 2026-06-18. Remove when FastAPI supports the
# listed fixed Starlette major versions. All other HIGH/CRITICAL findings fail CI.

# CVE-2026-48818: UNC-path SSRF/NTLM credential theft is Windows-specific.
# MailTube publishes Linux containers only and serves one operator-controlled
# static directory; no user-controlled filesystem roots are accepted.
CVE-2026-48818

# CVE-2026-54283: Starlette's application/x-www-form-urlencoded parsing limits
# can be bypassed. MailTube exposes JSON request bodies and does not call
# Request.form(), Form(), File(), or UploadFile anywhere in the application.
CVE-2026-54283
